  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you just learn enough, do enough scientific research, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] do not [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] be steeped in metaphysical thinking-- that means art became a way of life, in many ways, replaced religion-- religion at-- at the Austrian capital, although it was a Catholic country, and there were, of course, about 180,000 Jews.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But religion itself played a very minor role.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The middle class was, in many ways, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] living more with the arts than with-- with-- with religion.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was the-- let's say, the climate in which we grew up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm not trying to-- to make it sound idealistic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Of course, it was a pipe dream, as you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And if you read Kafka, you will find out that there were, of course, these thinkers, those who-- the artists, who have the gift-- and I should like to emphasize this-- they do not really live and work beyond their time.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Their art sees its own much clearer than the average people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "People in general know their past and very little of their presence.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's the artists who really project the presence.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That's why they always called-- they are ahead of their time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They aren't ahead of their time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They are with their time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And of course, if you read the great-- the great writers, you will look-- for instance, at the-- at the people who started painting-- if you look at Klimt's painting, if you look at [INAUDIBLE] painting, they were all part of this culture, which was so colorful in retrospect, of course.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I must say, when I was-- when World War I started, I had begun to-- to see this myself.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "My nose grew faster and bigger.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
